    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your<strong> tomato ketchup</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>BBQ sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
