    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>BBQ pork belly</strong> with the<strong> apple slaw</strong> and <strong>sweet potato chips</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> over the <strong>sliced BBQ pork belly</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
